data.description: Welcome to this beautiful ranch with finished basement featuring the very popular Amelia model located in the Aberdeen subdivision that offers a versatile floor plan based on your needs. Open-concept living space complete with a morning room, great room, and kitchen with large seating island, pantry, upgraded cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and new LVP flooring (2023). The first floor master bedroom includes an oversized walk-in closet. luxury shower and en suite bathroom. You'll love the conveniently located laundry room (Washer and Dryer Convey) that leads to a two-car garage. The first floor is complete with an additional bedroom and bathroom as well a dining room/study/OR 3rd bedroom if desired. Gorgeous upgraded staircase leads to the finished basement with rec room, full bathroom, and an additional 888 sq. ft of unfinished area that could be a possible 4th bedroom if needed (no egress window) and a spacious area for storage with sump pump/battery backup. Home is wired for a security system and all equipment stays.(Needs Activated). Newly installed deck (2023). Washer/Dryer 6/2023. Located on a cul de sac. Patio home living with HOA that includes all landscaping, and snow removal of the streets. Motivated Sellers.
